description.content:
Greetings!


Thanks for visiting my gig. I'm thrilled to create something amazing for you!


I'm Shibli Raihan, a passionate full-stack developer with 2 years of experience building remarkable websites for individuals, small businesses, and enterprises. Whether your starting fresh or upgrading your existing site, I'm here to turn your ideas into a stunning reality!


My Expertise Includes:


Front-End Development:

React.js | Next.js | Vue.js| Nuxt.js |TypeScript | JavaScript | CSS | HTML | jQuery


Back-End Development:

PHP (Laravel MVC) | Node.js (Express, Socket.io)


Databases:

MySQL


Styling Frameworks:

Tailwind CSS | Material-UI | Bootstrap | Styled-Components | Framer Motion


My Services:

  • Custom Application Development
  • REST API Integration
  • Feature-Rich Solutions
  • Application Maintenance
  • Responsive Front-end Design
  • Back-end API Development
  • Real-Time Web Applications (Socket.io)
  • Database Design and Optimization
  • Progressive Web Apps (PWAs)
  • E-commerce Development
  • Bug Fixing and Performance Optimization
  • Third-Party API Integration


What you will Provide?

  1.  Good architectural Product
  2.  Fast Delivery with source code
  3. Unlimited Review
  4.  Fully responsive Application
